name: MobiusZen's In-Between Expiramental Mixes (each unique)
description:
I'm mixing a ton of stuff to experiment, mostly aiming for a stylized 3D hoping for a unique style that comes from merging other styles, I figured I could share some of the better in between mixes as I go here. Each one will be different than others so the mixes are often not related, also I've really only tested these a bit to prod for what style they do on portraits, more testing needed for how they can do other things.

I figure my options are to share or not share, so this my attempt at sharing some of the steps along the process.
